%S A394066 0,3,60,2835,330598,99784390,81407472923
%N A394066 Number of directed paths in the n X n grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A394066 Excludes 0 length paths; including them increases each term by 1.
%C A394066 Number of undirected paths gives A394065. Number of directed paths not reduced for symmetry gives A288032*2.
%e A394066 a(2) = 3 (all symmetric and count as 1 each both undirected and directed):
%e A394066   +  +    +>>+    +>>+
%e A394066              v       v
%e A394066   +>>+    +  +    +<<+.
%e A394066 Nonsymmetric paths count as 2 each when directed, e.g.:
%e A394066   +  +--+      +  +>>+       +  +<<+
%e A394066         |            v             ^
%e A394066   +  +  +  ->  +  +  +  and  +  +  +
%e A394066         |            v             ^
%e A394066   +  +  +      +  +  +       +  +  +.
%o A394066 (PARI) \\ See Hohn link in A394065.
%Y A394066 Cf. A394065, A288032.
